Four days after giving birth, Khloé Kardashian has revealed that she and boyfriend Tristan Thompson have named their daughter True Kardashian added that she and Thompson are “overwhelmed with love” and that the bundle of joy has stolen their hearts. “Our little girl, True Thompson, has completely stolen our hearts and we are overwhelmed with LOVE. Such a blessing to welcome this angel into the family! Mummy and Daddy loooooove you True! (sic)” Kardashian’s post is her first since giving birth and news broke that her basketballer boyfriend had allegedly been cheating on her. READ MORE: Khloe Kardashian is pregnant Days before welcoming their baby girl, footage of Thompson with three different women surfaced online.  Kardashian and Thompson have yet to comment on the allegations. – Channel24